Philex provides extended functions for formatting, dynamically
repeating and cross-referencing numbered and named sentences,
with hyperref support. It is an addition to Wolfgang
Sternefeld's linguex package (adapted to version 4.3). 

Version: 1.2
Licence type: lppl

Author: Peter Pagin (with a contribution by Robin Fairbairns).
email: peter.pagin@philosophy.su.se
Date: 2014.03.28
